description:
We are thrilled to announce that DevFest will take place in Salalah this year. GDG Devfest Salalah brings together people who are shaping the future of Assistant, Web, IoT, AI and Cloud technologies for a day of sessions, workshops and networking.

It is a part of the IT conference series around the world for developers, students and tech enthusiasts to come together and get inspired from the latest technologies.

Our team creates DevFest to be the best place for inspiration and experience sharing. More about speakers, topics and agenda will be shared soon, visit >> Twitter or Instagram @GDG_Salalah

Can't wait to meet you in Salalah DevFest 2018! See you there.

name: UI/UX Design Workshop
description:
GDG Salalah is pleased to announce its first workshop in 2019! Which is UI/UX design workshop. The workshop will take place in PACA Salalah, for one week starts on 20 January till 24 January, from 4-7 PM each day.

Workshop language : Arabic
Workshop Level : Basic

Workshop will cover the following topics:

1. Introduction to website and mobile app UI/UX.
2. Visualize design recommendation via sketching.
3. Learn how to create website and mobile app Wireframes and Prototype.
4. Learn how to create user friendly website and mobile app mockups.
5. Introduction and best practices on Front-end prototyping tools, ex. Sketch, Fimga, Adobe XD, UXPin .. etc.
6. learn how to use design thinking and empathy map principles in UI/UX design.

P.S. Certificate will be provided to each participant on the completion of the workshop.

RSVP is now OPEN.

GDG Salalah Team,
